It seems there are several issues in your code. Let's address them one by one.

1. Incorrect import paths for components in `app-routing.module.ts`.

Update the import paths for `UserLoginComponent`, `PostCreateComponent`, and `PostListComponent`. Based on the error messages, the correct paths should be:
```typescript
import { UserRegistrationComponent } from './user-registration/user-registration.component';
import { UserLoginComponent } from './login/login.component';
import { PostCreateComponent } from './post-creation/post-creation.component';
import { PostListComponent } from './post-list/post-list.component';
```
1. Duplicate identifier errors in `app-routing.module.ts`.

It seems like you have some duplicate lines in your `app-routing.module.ts`. Remove the duplicate lines, and your imports should look like this:
```typescript
import { NgModule } from '@angular/core';
import { RouterModule, Routes } from '@angular/router';
import { UserRegistrationComponent } from './user-registration/user-registration.component';
import { UserLoginComponent } from './login/login.component';
import { PostCreateComponent } from './post-creation/post-creation.component';
import { PostListComponent } from './post-list/post-list.component';
```
1. Missing FormsModule import.

The errors related to `ngModel`, `ngForm`, and `ngSubmit` indicate that you might not have imported the `FormsModule` in your `app.module.ts`. Update your `app.module.ts` to import the `FormsModule`:
```typescript
import { BrowserModule } from '@angular/platform-browser';
import { NgModule } from '@angular/core';
import { FormsModule } from '@angular/forms'; // Add this line

import { AppRoutingModule } from './app-routing.module';
import { AppComponent } from './app.component';
import { UserRegistrationComponent } from './user-registration/user-registration.component';
import { UserLoginComponent } from './login/login.component';
import { PostCreateComponent } from './post-creation/post-creation.component';
import { PostListComponent } from './post-list/post-list.component';

@NgModule({
  declarations: [
    AppComponent,
    UserRegistrationComponent,
    UserLoginComponent,
    PostCreateComponent,
    PostListComponent
  ],
  imports: [
    BrowserModule,
    AppRoutingModule,
    FormsModule // Add this line
  ],
  providers: [],
  bootstrap: [AppComponent]
})
export class AppModule { }
```
After applying these changes, your application should compile and run without errors.
